  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A two months intervention in which two groups of cognitive disorders, Parkinson and
      Alzheimer's disease, will receive 50g/day of a commercial MCT supplement combined with
      supervised aerobic exercise 3 times/week. Cognition and ketones will be assess before and
      after the intervention, along with endocannabinoids plasma concentrations.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
